<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samasta bhuvanā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śraya śrīpṛthvīvalla
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bha mahārājādhirāja
<lb n="4"/>paramēśvara paramabha
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭṭārakaṁ satyāśraya
<lb n="6"/>kuḷatiḷakaṁ cāḷu<note n="46-1">The bottom portion of</note>
</p>

<!--<h4>Second face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mahēśvaraṁ sā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>hitya vidyāpā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rāyaṇa subha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṭa nārāyaṇaṁ vi 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>jayalakṣmī ni
<lb n="12" break="no"/>vāsaṁ kīrttivi
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ḷāsa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> paraca
<lb n="14" break="no"/>kravakranāha
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15"/>ddhi śrībhuvanaika
<lb n="16" break="no"/>malladēva pāda
<lb n="17"/>paṁkaja bhramaraṁ
<lb n="18"/>śrī matpaṁpa pe
<lb n="19" break="no"/>rmmānaḍigaḷu
<lb n="20"/>sakavaruṣa 99
<lb n="21" break="no"/>1 neya saumya
<lb n="22"/>saṁvatsarada pā(phā)
</p>

<!--<h4>Fourth Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="23" break="no"/>su(śu)bha caṁdra
<lb n="24"/>siddhāṁtadēva
<lb n="25" break="no"/>ra guḍḍa paḍa
<lb n="26" break="no"/>vaḷa cāvuṇḍa
<lb n="27" break="no"/>mayyaṁ mā
<lb n="28" break="no"/>ḍisida basa
<lb n="29" break="no"/>dige khaṁḍa
<lb n="30"/>sphuṭita <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

